观看 Tyler, The Creator 与 Kendrick Lamar 和 Baby Keem 一起进行“The Hillbillies”现场首演https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tyler-the-creator-join-kendrick-lamar-baby-keem-for-the-hillbillies-live-debut-3537152?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=观看创作者泰勒加入肯德里克·拉马尔宝贝基姆的乡巴佬现场首演Elizabeth AubreySun, 12 Nov 2023 19:12:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3537152 <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒，造物主、肯德里克·拉马尔和贝比·基姆" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这三位艺术家都一起出现在泰勒一年一度的洛杉矶音乐节上</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tyler-the-creator-join-kendrick-lamar-baby-keem-for-the-hillbillies-live-debut-3537152">观看 Tyler, The Creator 与 Kendrick Lamar 和 Baby Keem 一起进行“The Hillbillies”现场首秀的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒，造物主、肯德里克·拉马尔和贝比·基姆" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Tyler-The-Creator-Kendrick-Lamar-and-Baby-Keem-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（11 月 11 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">，Tyler, The Creator</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/baby-keem">Baby Keem</a>一起参加了“The Hillbillies”的现场首秀。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tyler-the-creator-call-me-if-you-get-lost-review-2979669">泰勒，创造者——《如果你迷路了就打电话给我》评论：一封写给造就他的流派的情书</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-baby-keem-the-hillbillies-bon-iver-single-3449969">拉马尔和贝比·基姆以《The Hillbillies》为歌迷带来了惊喜</a>，这是一首以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">Bon Iver 为样本的受钻探启发的新歌曲。</a>这首单曲是两人继<a href="/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖作品《Family Ties》以及 2021 年的《Range Brothers》和《Vent》之后第十次合作。</p><p>在这首歌的视频中，造物主泰勒也客串了一把，他在镜头前闪过一个按钮，上面写着“Camp Flog Gnaw Carnival 2023”——这是拉马尔和基姆第一次非官方宣布将出现在泰勒的年度歌曲中。洛杉矶音乐节。</p><p>昨晚，当三人都登台表演这首歌时，事实证明了这一点。您可以在这里观看这一刻： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="乡下人 CAMP FLOG GNAW 2023" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-4b9jIBwACk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tyler-the-creator-unveils-schedule-for-camp-flog-gnaw-carnival-3537080">，造物主泰勒透露了本周末（11 月 11 日至 12 日）举行的 Camp Flog Gnaw 嘉年华的完整时间表。</a></p><p>预计出演的艺人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/willow-smith">Willow</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/balming-tiger">Balming Tiger</a> 。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tyler-the-creator-unveils-schedule-for-camp-flog-gnaw-carnival-3537080">在此处</a>查看完整的时间表。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tyler-the-creators-camp-flog-gnaw-festival-off-for-2022-returning-in-2023-3322060">Camp Flog Gnaw 将在平静几年后回归</a>，泰勒的经纪人克里斯·克兰西此前曾表示，其原因“其实并不那么深奥”。</p><p> “泰勒全年都在巡演，并忙于许多项目。阅读了茶叶以及疫情结束后的节日活动，我们认为最好明年再回来，”他说。</p><p> 2019 年的版本中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/solange">Solange</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA twigs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brockhampton">Brockhampton</a>等人登上了舞台。虽然有传言称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-ocean">弗兰克·奥森</a>将出演未透露姓名的令人惊讶的头条新闻，但事实证明是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">德雷克</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tyler-the-creator-join-kendrick-lamar-baby-keem-for-the-hillbillies-live-debut-3537152">观看 Tyler, The Creator 与 Kendrick Lamar 和 Baby Keem 一起进行“The Hillbillies”现场首秀的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
视频重新出现后，索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特为过去对罗比·威廉姆斯的“残忍”行为道歉https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextor-apologises-for-being-cruel-to-robbie-williams-in-the-past-3537142?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sophie-埃利斯·贝斯特为过去对罗比·威廉姆斯的残忍行为道歉Elizabeth AubreySun, 12 Nov 2023 18:44:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3537142 <p><img width="1986" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特和罗比·威廉姆斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams.jpg 1986w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-400x256.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-800x512.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-696x445.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-1392x890.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-1068x683.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1986px) 100vw, 1986px" /></p><p>埃利斯-贝斯特透露，她“几年前”向威廉姆斯道歉，从那时起，他们“一起创作了一些歌曲”</p><p>视频重新出现后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextor-apologises-for-being-cruel-to-robbie-williams-in-the-past-3537142">，Sophie Ellis-Bextor 为过去对罗比·威廉姆斯的“残忍”行为道歉，该视频</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1986" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特和罗比·威廉姆斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams.jpg 1986w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-400x256.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-800x512.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-696x445.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-1392x890.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sophie-Ellis-Bextor-and-Robbie-Williams-1068x683.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1986px) 100vw, 1986px" /></p><p>在威廉姆斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/robbie-williams-review-netflix-3532889">最近的 Netflix 纪录片</a>中重新出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sophie-ellis-bextor">埃利斯-贝斯特的一段视频后，索菲·</a>埃利斯-贝斯特为对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>的“残忍”行为道歉。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/soundtrack-of-my-life-sophie-ellis-bextor-2836919">阅读更多：《我的生活》原声带 – 索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（11 月 12 日），埃利斯-贝斯特在 Instagram 的新帖子中针对这段视频向威廉姆斯道歉，并表示她“几年前”曾联系过他，并给他写了一封“便条”道歉。</p><p>埃利斯-贝斯特表示，从那时起，两人就成为了朋友，她还透露，他们甚至“一起创作了一些歌曲”。</p><p>她在 Instagram 上写道：“1998 年，19 岁的我对 @robbiewilliams 非常无礼，他精彩的 Netflix 纪录片中收录了我的可怕片段。我不需要再看到它就感到难过。自从我说出这句话以来的25年里，我真的对自己的说话方式感到很糟糕。</p><p> “我当时认为表现得像个傻瓜很聪明，但当时并不酷，现在看到它更糟糕。不骄傲。不是我抚养孩子的方式。话虽这么说，我想伸出援手并道歉，所以几年前我找到了罗比的地址，并给他写了一张便条，表达我的歉意。他非常仁慈和宽容。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CzjaqUYso3q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;