r-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Millie-Bobbie-Brown-new-trailer-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Millie-Bobbie-Brown-new-trailer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2002px) 100vw, 2002px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>分享了由<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/damsel"><em>米莉·鲍比·布朗</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/millie-bobby-brown">(Millie Bobby Brown)</a>主演的《少女》的戏剧性新预告片 - 请观看下面的剪辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/enola-holmes-2-review-netflix-3337706">《伊诺拉·福尔摩斯 2》评论：一个值得解开的曲折谋杀之谜</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影由胡安·卡洛斯·弗雷斯纳迪略执导，丹·马佐编剧，讲述了布朗饰演的“少女”嫁给“英俊王子”的故事，这似乎是一个童话故事的开始。然而，布朗扮演的角色很快意识到她将被牺牲，必须尝试与龙战斗才能生存。</p><p>罗宾·赖特 (Robin Wright) 饰演的女王对布朗饰演的角色说道：“世世代代以来，保护我们的人民一直是我们的任务。所以今晚，你将加入一长串帮助建立这个王国的女性行列……代价是昂贵的，但回报也是如此。”</p><p> Netflix 的官方剧情简介如下：“一位孝顺的少女同意嫁给一位英俊的王子，却发现王室已将她招募为祭品，以偿还古老的债务。被扔进一个与喷火龙一起的山洞里，她必须依靠自己的智慧和意志才能生存。”</p><p>在预告片中，可以看到布朗逃离了龙，然后用剑与它战斗。</p><p> Set for release in 2024, the film also stars Nick Robinson, Angela Bassett, Ray Winstone, Brooke Carter and Shohreh Aghdashloo.</p><p> Check out the full trailer here: </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="少女|官方预告片 | Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9eN_AGX8GXk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> This summer, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/millie-bobby-brown-says-shes-ready-to-move-on-from-stranger-things-3483421">Brown said she is ready to move on from <em>Stranger T</em> <em>h</em> <em>ings.</em></a></p><p> The British actor, who has played Eleven since she was 11-years-old, said in a new interview that she is ready for the Netflix show to end.</p><p> She told <em><a href="https://wwd.com/eye/people/millie-bobby-brown-fragrance-wildly-me-stranger-things-book-wedding-planning-1235762447" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Women&#39;s Wear Daily</a></em> : “I think I&#39;m ready. It&#39;s been such a huge factor in part of my life, but it&#39;s like graduating high school, it&#39;s like senior year.</p><p> “You&#39;re ready to go and blossom and flourish and you&#39;re grateful for the time you&#39;ve had, but it&#39;s time to create your own message and live your own life.”</p><p> Along with <em>Stranger Things,</em> she has featured in two <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/enola-holmes-2-review-netflix-3337706">Enola Holmes</a> and <em>Godzilla</em> movies.</p><p> Meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-harbour-provides-update-on-stranger-things-season-five-3481695">David Harbour recently provided an update</a> on the final season of <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>Stranger Things</em></a> in <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/david-harbour-gran-turismo-stranger-things-lily-allen-3479934">an exclusive interview with <em>NME</em></a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-millie-bobby-brown-fight-dragon-in-new-trailer-for-damsel-3537066">Watch Millie Bobby Brown fight a dragon in dramatic new trailer for &#39;Damsel&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
